Donovan Edward RUBY, Appellant, v. SECRETARY OF the UNITED STATES NAVY, Appellee. No. 20473. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. Dec. 19, 1966. See also 9 Cir., 365 F.2d 385. Donovan Edward Ruby, in pro. per. Cecil F. Poole, U. S. Atty., Jerry K. Cimmet, Asst. U. S. Atty., San Francisco, Cal., for appellee.

*405Before JERTBERG and DUNIWAY, Circuit Judges, and CROCKER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

The motion of the United States to affirm is granted, and the judgment appealed from is affirmed.
